metadata.name: Dem Apples #1
metadata.description: A collection of 5500 NFTs brought to you by painter and visual artist, Griffin Goodman. Dem Apples are fun, playful, full of joy, goofy, and designed to inspire. We are a community for everyone, a place for creatives and collectors to come together, to foster ideas, projects, and relationships. We're creating a fusion between the physical and metaverse - and we can't wait for you all to be apart of it.
